.SH "NAME"
optiups \- Driver for Opti\-UPS (Viewsonic) UPS and Zinto D (ONLINE\-USV) equipment
.SH "SYNOPSIS"
.sp
\fBoptiups\fR \-h
.sp
\fBoptiups\fR \-a \fIUPS_NAME\fR [\fIOPTIONS\fR]
